farsight2: farsight2 (Farsight Communications Framework)
farsight2:
farsight2: Farsight is an effort to create a framework to deal with all known 
farsight2: audio/video conferencing protocols for use by applications such as 
farsight2: instant messaging. These applications are able to use Farsight for 
farsight2: all their Audio/Video conferencing needs without having to worry 
farsight2: about any of the lower level streaming and NAT traversal issues.  
farsight2:
farsight2: Farsight forms an integral part of the Telepathy framework.
farsight2:
